Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那里就是第七师团的大本营
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.75,0:00:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,窗户上有铁栏杆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,入口处整晚都有卫兵把守
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.46,0:00:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,现在去救他可能也来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,打不死的杉元这次运气该到头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,杉元一定还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他的强大在于不会被死的恐惧所打败的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,敢冲进棕熊巢穴的人除了父亲我还不认识第二个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他通过主动走到死神的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.32,0:00:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,来找到活下去的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.91,0:00:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他才是打不死的杉元
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:11.81,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\pos(1506,854.1)\blur7.5}疾驰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:15.82,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1506,854.1)\fad(0,700)\t(0,500,\c&HFFFFFF&)\blur7.5}疾驰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.32,0:02:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,说了不许打死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把你剁碎了喂猪!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,还好有人过来 捡了一条命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,本来想把你们兄弟俩一起送去见阎王!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.04,0:02:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不要让那对兄弟靠近杉元
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你们来得太晚了 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我故意闹出这么大动静
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,倒是给我快点冲进来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙太疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他可真是结实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,杉元还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,既然关在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那文身人皮应该被他藏起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.36,0:03:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那道铁栏旧得生锈了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,只要折断一根 我就能让关节脱臼钻进去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢赌博
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这次把赌注下在你们身上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,帮你救杉元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是金子要有我的份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我对金子没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了你就和杉元分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好 成交
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,用绳子牵住外面的马
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,让马跑起来拉动铁栏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,整个铁栏拉垮 就能一口气逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你带了肥皂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,往身上涂些肥皂 就更好钻过铁栏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,没肥皂 油倒是有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:53.83,Explain,,0,0,0,,这是一种用熊的胃制成的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,棕熊的油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那对双胞胎肯定还会来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,再不想想办法 下次来我绝对会死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,越狱王白石
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么在这
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一个凶巴巴的阿伊努姑娘用毒箭威胁我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,阿希莉帕姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这次又是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,马在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,偷马贼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是列塔拉的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,被马发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不好 有麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,别管了 快把我手铐解了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,浩平在外面看着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不许任何人进去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,打死他再给他解绑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,就能扯理由说他想逃跑 我们只能打死他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 洋平 枪给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,枪声会被其他人听到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:04:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,用刺刀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没牙的杂种
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这回我认出来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,打开门就发现…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,里面已经是这副惨状了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,肠子都出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,活不了多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,简直就是风前烛火啊 杉元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,救我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,文身人皮拿去便是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,准备马橇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,送杉元去市里最好的医院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕用枪顶在医生的脑门上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,也要把他叫起来给杉元疗伤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会尽全力救你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你也别忘了报答我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得自己快死的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要告诉我文身人皮藏哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝对不会死!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我会跟在你们后面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,记得要不停地和杉元说话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,听好 要在他死之前问出人皮下落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这具尸体真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,右手的伤口很深
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.91,0:06:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,防卫时受的伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那应该拿不动刺刀才对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,左手明明没受伤 为什么不换左手拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:07:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的是用这只右手和杉元互刺吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说是杉元把刺刀放在尸体手上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这条皮带
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,连背面都有沾血的指纹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么杀了他以后要给他系好皮带 杉元
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,谁掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他偷走了肠子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑 快快快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这匹马出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没听到枪声
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这道伤口是怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,毒全在里面 不能吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉 有人放火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,请站远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,会引爆弹药库的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还是让杉元他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不 让杉元他们一伙收集人皮更快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他们棋高一着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:09:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,火势蔓延得太快 文身人皮没有抢救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,人皮没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.22,0:09:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,害得我热死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,热死了热死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,难怪我找了半天没找着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这个变态中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,阿希莉帕姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,本想耍个帅 一个人走掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,却被你救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我太丢人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我准备了一些资金
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,还有几杆洋人造的最新式枪支
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我能做的只有这些事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我这把骨头要是再利索点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,已经老到不能和你一起东奔西走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,少胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,为新撰组执着到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你的血不可能没有滚烫起来 永仓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,永仓?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这老头难道是人称新撰组最强剑士的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,永仓新八?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 新撰组的老不死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的目的可不只是单纯的金子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 这匹马该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,什么怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,扔下不管就可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你看 还这么亲我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不 带上它会引人注意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,处理掉更好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想奖励列塔拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,说到马肉当然是樱锅啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,樱锅?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,用寿喜烧的方式料理马肉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,东京流行这么吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,寿喜烧?好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,要做樱锅就少不了鸡蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找附近的农户要一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,尴尬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.11,0:11:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,杉元 你的脸受了不小的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,身上也伤痕累累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.07,0:11:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,阿希莉帕姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找黄金就要面对这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你有个什么万一 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.75,0:11:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我没脸见你外婆还有村子里的其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你想说我是累赘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不 也不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:11:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,贴在脸上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:11:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,据说马肉有消肿的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我的父亲已经惨死在他人的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我早就知道会有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得和杉元一起行动 或许就能达到我的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我自己做出的判断我自己决定帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,而把我当成小孩 不把我当成搭档去信任
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人擅自行动然后被抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人是你才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,除了鸡蛋 我还要到了卷心菜和牛蒡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至还分我了一些糖 酱油和酒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你们之间搞得很僵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,马上要吃大餐了好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 夫妻吵架狗都不爱理 我才懒得管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,美美地吃上一顿火锅 重归于好怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,等肉变成樱花色就能吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,蘸上打好的鸡蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.07,0:12:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃 这味道绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,清淡的马肉和浓郁的味噌最配了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,味噌做底料棒到不能再棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这个放了欧索玛?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 欧索玛?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,阿希莉帕姑娘 是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.22,0:13:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,樱锅不能缺味噌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,阿希莉帕妹妹不喜欢味噌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,何止是不喜欢 她以为那是屎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,屎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,和人和阿伊努
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.40,0:13:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到在这种地方无法相互理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 阿希莉帕姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,肉还有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这次不加味噌 重新做一锅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,阿希…莉帕姑娘?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(860.999,975.499)}欧索玛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,屎真好吃!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,说了不是屎啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不懂你们在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不过你很喜欢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,欣那欣那
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,必须欣那
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我还要欧索玛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,等下要见的涩川善治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是一帮山贼的头头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算让他们所有人入伙?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,白天我派过去的使者没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.55,0:14:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所以直接找上门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,人数我们不占优啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,人数从来都不叫优势
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,能够充当战斗力的只有视死如归的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,想活下去 那就先做好死人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 门都不敲一下就进来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,小伙挺帅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,来 举高高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,涩川 我派了人来找你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 把他打了一顿 他什么都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,阿伊努的黄金 听起来很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看你的文身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是你安排在外面的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是帮忙 还是动手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,自己选一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,服了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,动手!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:16:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一个都别想出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是新撰组副长的鬼之面相吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,都说人到了该死的时候不死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那就比死还要屈辱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,到了这个年纪还想发动战争
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,正常人是干不出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,土方先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.28,0:16:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是想找个可以安心去死的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是打算再活一百年的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的要重建新撰组吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我只对金子感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会相信占领北海道这种梦话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,想让虾夷独立的人多得是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:17:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他们很久以前就住在这片土地上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,拉屎王去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,白石去城里搜集情报了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我暂时不要靠近那里比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看 杉元 是虾夷鹿的脚印
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,痕迹还很新
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.08,0:17:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那就追过去吧 阿希莉帕姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,虾夷鹿好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.96,0:17:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,脑花撒点盐 好吃的 杉元
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,杉元 你太慢了 我们会追不上鹿的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 好累
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,水 想喝水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这个席萨姆好丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,杉元 我找到好东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,弥猴梨的藤蔓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,它的藤蔓吸水性很强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,砍断它会溢出大量树液
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在山里如果水喝光了 可以拿它代替
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗳 我也要喝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,阿希莉帕姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,让我喝一口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 好大的力气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,弥猴梨的藤蔓还有其他用处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我穿的鞋托就是用它做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这个不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,阿希莉帕姑娘?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,看 杉元
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,雄鹿在这里磨角
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,宣告这里是自己的地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,用棍子摩擦这棵树发出声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,雄鹿可能会回来查看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么瞎用苏图啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,芙奇说 以前的鹿要更多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,很容易就能逮到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为我们阿伊努不把鹿当成神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,而是用猎物的意思称呼它们为“与库”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,也是因为它们很好抓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们认为与库是神撒到人间 送给我们的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是某年冬天 下起了一场鹿都刨不出食物的大雪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,死了很多鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.86,0:19:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是因为有人不珍惜它们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以神一怒之下 不往人间撒鹿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.83,0:19:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真的来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,壮得像一匹马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.84,0:19:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,安静 慢慢行动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,没打中要害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.47,0:19:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们追 上山
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.73,0:19:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,找那些带血的竹叶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,出了灌木丛就找脚印
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 怪我一时心急
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这样只会给那只鹿徒增痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要了结它的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一条狗和两个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一个男人是个大块头 走路很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,受伤的是右脚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,和北海道的棕熊比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,东北又鬼打的那些黑熊简直就是狗遇到了狼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这条狗是阿伊努人培育的犬种 连棕熊都不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.98,0:20:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那把村田枪一次只能装一发子弹 太不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.82,0:20:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这不叫坚持 而是过时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,军人兄弟手上的枪能装五发子弹对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,的确方便
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好 龙 给我上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.21,0:20:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是母熊就干了它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你别出手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.67,0:20:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我和棕熊之间的决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 备用的子弹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:21:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,用村田枪的猎户都会把备用子弹夹在手指间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有五发子弹就会误以为自己有五次决斗的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,一发子弹才能壮胆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,面对面站在熊从巢穴里冲出来的位置 成功吓到了熊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,吓得呆站着就是你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.54,0:21:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,又鬼家的谷垣你 还要跟着我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是见你躺在雪地里 把你救了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可不是想要个老伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.89,0:21:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你也在追那条白狼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我在家乡的时候 曾经听一个卖药郎说过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.69,0:21:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,北海道有一个技术高超的“猎熊人”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,据说那个人上了哪座山
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.28,0:21:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哪座山的熊就会消失干净
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.40,0:22:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.74,0:22:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,二瓶铁造
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.88,0:23:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 猎户之魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.02,0:01:00.94,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}I realize desire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.11,0:01:04.53,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}And trembling in the anger
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.61,0:01:08.61,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}Though I know that you're a great liar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.70,0:01:12.28,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}The world is painted in dark grey
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:19.00,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}混乱の時代や嘘と暴力の螺旋が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,0:01:26.97,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}どうか貴方の未来へと陰落とさぬ様に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.09,0:01:34.39,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}Going down to reach somewhere together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.43,0:01:40.65,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}もう一度 夢見るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.65,0:01:43.82,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}Someday we will find out the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:51.07,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}この傷の数だけ 闇夜を駆け抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.45,0:01:54.74,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}踊る Long and winding road
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.08,0:01:58.29,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}Standing on the cutting edge of life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:02.13,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}Holding a rusty old knife
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:05.67,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}朝陽が射し示すまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.96,0:02:09.34,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}駆ける Long and winding road
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.02,0:01:00.94,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}欲望在我心中咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.11,0:01:04.53,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}我在愤怒中颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.61,0:01:08.61,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}尽管我知道你是个大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.70,0:01:12.28,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}世界却早已被染上一层深灰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:19.00,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}这个混乱的时代 交织着谎言与暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,0:01:26.97,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}希望它们不要为你的未来蒙上阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.09,0:01:34.39,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}让我们一起坚持 抵达一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.43,0:01:40.65,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}然后再做一次梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.65,0:01:43.82,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}有一天我们会找到真相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:51.07,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}有多少伤痕 便跨过多少黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.45,0:01:54.74,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}在这条漫长曲折的路上起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.08,0:01:58.29,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}拼搏在生死一线间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:02.13,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}握住那生锈的旧匕首
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:05.67,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}直至晨光洒向大地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.96,0:02:09.34,OP-Cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}在这条漫长曲折的路上奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.55,0:23:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.17,0:23:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.86,0:22:20.60,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,夜を刺す無数の遠吠えが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:24.77,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,天を貫いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.20,0:22:30.91,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,僕らみんなたった一つの満月に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:35.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,そうやって手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:39.62,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,目的地の消された地図持って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.62,0:22:42.14,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,燃える炎 交わし合って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.14,0:22:45.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,荒れた未来図は 続いてるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.32,0:22:49.82,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,痛みもぜんぶ受け取って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.85,0:22:57.23,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,連れていくんだと 深く胸に誓って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.26,0:22:59.47,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,ぶつかって 傷付いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:02.21,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,いつかまた、ここに来るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.24,0:23:04.66,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,一切の現実も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:08.93,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,燃え尽きれば美しい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.46,0:23:13.75,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,駆け抜ける 白の世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.78,0:23:21.97,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,迷いを捨てた火花が今、散った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.86,0:22:20.60,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,将夜晚刺穿的无数嗷叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:24.77,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,贯穿了天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.20,0:22:30.91,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,我们大家都向着唯一的满月
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:35.29,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,像这样将手伸出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:39.62,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,拿着被消去目的地的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.62,0:22:42.14,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,燃烧的火焰互相交错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.14,0:22:45.29,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,未来虽然还模糊 但还是会继续
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.32,0:22:49.82,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,哪怕需要承受全部的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.85,0:22:57.23,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,也要将其带走深深地在胸中发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.26,0:22:59.47,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,历经挫折受过伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:02.21,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,总有一天会再来到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.24,0:23:04.66,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,现实的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:08.93,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,付之一炬 才是美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.46,0:23:13.75,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,奔跑在这纯白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.78,0:23:21.97,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,舍弃迷茫的火花绚烂绽放在这一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.55,0:23:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,
